'''Codbixin''' ({{lang-en|Voting}}; {{lang-ar|تصويت}}) waa nidaamka koox dad ah ku doortaan hogaamiye (sida [[Madaxweyne]], [[ra'iisul wasaare|Ra'iisalwasaare]], xubin ka tirsan golle iyo wixii la mid ah). Sida caadiga ah waxaa jirta dhowr arimood oo ka horeysa codbixinta. Marka ugu horeeysa qof ayaa isa-soo-sharaxa, ka dib dadka u soo bandhiga ''sababta uu ugu qalmo jagadaasi''. Markaas ka dib ayaa doorasho la qabbtaa taasi oo loo codbixiyo dhowr musharax ee tartanka ku jiray.

==Hordhac==
Codbixintu waa nidaam ka mid ah [[doorasho|doorashada]] lagu doorto qof ama koox jago ka qabata meel. Doorashadu waxay noqon kartaa mid [[siyaasad]]ed ama mid bulsho, sida ganacsi, urur ama koox kale oo ka mid ah bulshada.

==Siyaasada==
Marka laga hadlayo codbixinta waxaa muhiim ah in marka hore meesha jirto [[dimoqraadi]]yad u ogol shacabka ineey dhiibtaan codkooda.

